Thanks for all the community support so far! Weâ€™re doing some final auto testing, using the 2023 PathPlanner beta. When we set the Alliance to Blue in Driver Station, our paths work fine. However, when we switch the Alliance to Red in driver station, the paths done flip as expected. We have the robot move from right to left in our auto in Blue, but itâ€™s also moving from right to left on Red, when to should go left to right. This is using the 2022 field. Did we miss some config to get it to handle alliance selection correctly?
